  "texts": [
    "Based on these outcomes, it is evident that the RCA network demonstrates commendable performance across all three datasets.",
    "However, its efficacy varies, achieving optimal results with the PatternNet dataset, while showing comparatively lower performance on the RSSCN7 and EuroSAT datasets.",
    "The RCA network's superior performance on PatternNet can be ascribed to notable inter-class distinctions and substantial intra-class similarities.",
    "The clearly defined boundaries between classes in PatternNet enable the network to accurately capture unique features within each category.",
    "Additionally, the RCA model's channel-attention mechanism enhances the model's ability to identify variations in scale and orientation within the dataset, as well as to discern details at a granular level."
  ],
